{"tid":793650,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"篤左人背脊⋯⋯良心好不安","createTime":"2018-08-25T14:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T17:22:50.000Z","uid":58841,"like":17,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0c3dd6958b024394bc25a4aa553f2b2970616e","tid":793650,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:49:01.000Z","msg":"咁琴日我就去左其他舖頭做helper<br />\n就睇住另一個舖頭既helper incharge玩足成日電話<br />\n鑒於我之前challenge過另一個同事點解你可以當住個客面玩電話<br />\n佢屌鳩我話係公司野 之後仲要俾佢針住<br />\n（雖然條撚樣成日想搏升職但係公司唔睇好佢走左）<br />\n咁今次我就好識做<br />\n直頭望到佢個mon真係遊戲畫面黎 仲要企係cashier度玩<br />\n結果個日全日既單全部都係我同另一個同事開 佢唔知做乜鳩<br />\n但係諗諗下唔想做篤人背脊咁仆街 只係覺得呢間舖條數死撚梗<br />\n同埋唔想去尊重佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果今日返到自己舖吹吹下水唔覺意同個sotre man爆左出黎<br />\n佢就話要我做證人同上頭講 又望到佢地舖條數低到仆街<br />\n我只係個PT仔唔好咁玩我好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18ad2fb2763d354c92b604034ef648c5b086e70","tid":793650,"uid":21423,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:50:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b497f7b4458b02554524d1e694e3cc2c7735446","tid":793650,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a18ad2fb2763d354c92b604034ef648c5b086e70","tid":793650,"uid":21423,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:50:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb19eac6c0ae68f2f3726f62922244ca9ff794f","tid":793650,"uid":133375,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:52:44.000Z","msg":"做pt做到你咁閪<br />\n間鋪爆數你都冇得分架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9c92097736bc7c75f9784ae645af4cc693349f","tid":793650,"uid":7183,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:53:09.000Z","msg":"攪屎棍未你依d"},{"pid":"aeb6d52b409211c72d1ebee15aff737180870a53","tid":793650,"uid":76098,"like":0,"d